TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time in the day when the float ended it descent to parking
TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when park pressure is reached  (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_2.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time in the day when the float first activated the valve during its descent
TECH_PARAM_2.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when first stabilization appears during descent to park (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_3.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time in the day when the float started its descent to profile depth
TECH_PARAM_3.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the beginning of the descent to profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_4.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time in the day when the float achieved its profile depth
TECH_PARAM_4.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the end of the descent to profile depth.

TECH_PARAM_5.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time in the day when the float started it s ascending profile
TECH_PARAM_5.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of minutes elapsed in the day at the beginning of the ascent to the surface.

TECH_PARAM_6.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time in the day when the float ended it s ascending profile
TECH_PARAM_6.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: ascent end time, just before Argos transmission  - note units can vary and the raw values can be in the tech file only if it's not possible to calculate the final JULD in real time.

TECH_PARAM_7.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of valve activations at surface
TECH_PARAM_7.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of solenoid valve actions at the surface until the crossing of the GAP threshold

TECH_PARAM_8.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of valve activations during the descent to parking
TECH_PARAM_8.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_9.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump activations during the descent to parking
TECH_PARAM_9.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_10.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of valve activations during the descent to profile
TECH_PARAM_10.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_11.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump activations during the descent to profile
TECH_PARAM_11.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_12.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of pump activations during the ascent to surface
TECH_PARAM_12.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between start and end of ascent

TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of depth corrections during parking
TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy during park phase - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_14.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of entries in parking zone
TECH_PARAM_14.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Cumulated numbers of entries in both parking zones (at park and profile depth). Specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target park/profile pressure (thus 2 is the nominal value for a float which never experienced stabilization issues).

TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of CTD points in descent profile
TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of slices of the descending profile after reduction

TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of messages in descent profile
TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets used to transmit data collected during the descent phases (from surface to the parking depth and from the parking depth to the profile depth).

TECH_PARAM_17.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of CTD points in ascent profile

TECH_PARAM_18.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of messages in ascent profile
TECH_PARAM_18.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets used to transmit data collected during the ascent from the profile depth to the surface.

TECH_PARAM_19.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of CTD points in parking

TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Iridium packets used to transmit data collected during the drift at park depth.

TECH_PARAM_21.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of hydraulic packets used to transmit hydraulic (pump or valve) actions performed during the cycle.

TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Surface pressure measured just before the float dives which is then used to correct pressure on board the float for the next profile.  Note: this is a relative offset and no further correction is possible. Autocorrected

TECH_PARAM_24.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: is the float beached? - could be logical

TECH_PARAM_25.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: grounded flag , diagnostic bit - could also be logical?  Yes/no? 0/1? Or can be number of profiles during which the float grounded

TECH_PARAM_26.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: battery voltage during inactive surface phase

TECH_PARAM_29.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag for Error on CTD Fast Pressure Command

TECH_PARAM_30.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag for Error on CTD Start Profile Command

TECH_PARAM_31.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag for Error on CTD Stop Profile Command

TECH_PARAM_32.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag for Error on CTD Download Command

TECH_PARAM_33.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Flag for Error on CTD Average Command

TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of incoming Iridium packets received during previous session
TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of Incoming Iridium Packets Received during previous session

TECH_PARAM_37.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Day of month of last GPS fix
TECH_PARAM_37.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day of month of last GPS fix/Time of Last GPS Fix (HH)

TECH_PARAM_38.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Day of month of last GPS fix/Time of Last GPS Fix (HH)

TECH_PARAM_40.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Wake-up by watchdog alarm (Yes or No)

TECH_PARAM_41.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of hydraulic (pump or valve) actions performed during the cycle. Due to transmission limitations some of them may not be transmitted (in the NUMBER_HydraulicPackets_COUNT transmitted packets).

TECH_PARAM_42.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: the number of seconds required to obtain a GPS fix for a profile

TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Time needed to transmit last Housekeeping packet
TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time required to transmit the last housekeeping message

TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of power resets DO sensor
TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of power resets of the DO sensor

TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Number of failed acquisitions DO sensor
TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of failed  acquisitions of the DO sensor
